data.description: Price reduction below market value! This lovely corner lot home is located in a senior citizen community with two bedrooms, one bath, one car garage, and the potential for RV parking. The home comes with an enclosed patio and a big backyard both great for hanging out and entertainment. This home has 2 sheds in the back yard. The laundry room is separate and big enough located next to the enclosed patio.   Adorable home.  The property is a probate sale.
